You have now practiced breath and self observation in multiple rounds.

79
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:43,040
And you can take such practice with you to any place, any time, where you can pause and practice for any period of time, even 40 seconds or 1 minute or 3 minutes or 5 minutes.

80
00:27:43,040 --> 00:28:06,040
Whether you are waiting for a train or inside a bus, if you are sitting in an office,

81
